cl-state-sync
=============

This library was extracted from the CLPIC (Common Lisp P2P Intellectual
Property Chain) project.

Extracted module: src/sync/state/

The extraction includes functionality for:
- Snapshot-based state synchronization
- UTXO set recovery
- State trie reconstruction
- Merkle proof verification

This is a standalone library with no external dependencies beyond SBCL.

